ber 2015}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name = Weekend Kitchen with Waitrose\n| image = \n| genre = \n| presenter = [[Lisa Snowdon]]<br>[[Steve Jones (presenter)|Steve Jones]]<br>[[Angellica Bell]] <small>(1 episode)</small>\n| country = United Kingdom\n| language = English\n| num_series = 2\n| num_episodes = 19\n| runtime = 60 minutes <small>(inc. adverts)</small>\n| company = [[Spun Gold]]\n| distributor =\n| network = [[Channel 4]]\n| picture_format = [[16:9]] [[576i]] [[Standard-definition television|SDTV]]\n| first_aired = {{start date|df=y|2014|4|26}}\n| last_aired = {{start date|df=y|2014|12|20}}\n}}\n\n'''''Weekend Kitchen with Waitrose''''' is a British [[Lifestyle (sociology)|lifestyle]] show that has aired on [[Channel 4]] since 26 April and is hosted by [[Lisa Snowdon]] and [[Steve Jones (presenter)|Steve Jones]]. [[Angellica Bell]] filled in for Snowdon for one episode on 21 June 2014.\n\n==Transmissions==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Series !! Start date !! End date !! Episodes\n|-\n| '''1''' || 26 April 2014 || 12 July 2014 || 12\n|-\n| '''2''' || 20 September 2014 || 20 December 2014 || 14\n|-\n|}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.channel4.com/programmes/weekend-kitchen-with-waitrose Official Website]\n*[https://twitter.com/wkndkitchen Official Twitter]\n*[https://www.facebook.com/WeekendKitchenwithWaitrose Official Facebook]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Weekend Kitchen with Waitrose}}\n[[Category:2010s British television series]]\n[[Category:2014 British television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2014 British television series endings]]\n[[Category:British cooking television programmes]]\n[[Category:Channel 4 television programmes]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Waitrose]]\n", "name_user": "LittleWink", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toSteve Jones(link changed toSteve Jones (Welsh presenter); link changed toSteve Jones (Welsh presenter)) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikip