ood Game Night.|date=August 15, 2018 |accessdate=March 27, 2019}}</ref>\n| Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Host for a Reality or Reality-Competition Program\n| ''[[Hollywood Game Night]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=2|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actress in a Comedy Series\n| rowspan=3|''[[The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2019\n| rowspan=2 {{won}}\n|-\n| Screen Actors Guild Award\n| Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Comedy Series\n|-\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n===Film===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Title\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Role\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n!scope=col class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n|''Taxi Killer''\n| rowspan=2|1988\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|''[[Vice Versa (1988 film)|Vice Versa]]''\n| Ms. Linstrom\n|\n|\n|-\n|''[[Straight Talk]]''\n| 1992\n| Gladys\n| Voice role\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Fugitive (1993 film)|The Fugitive]]''\n|  rowspan=2|1993\n| Dr. Kathy Wahlund\n|\n|\n|-\n|''[[Fatal Instinct]]''\n| Prison Reporter\n|\n|\n|-\n|''[[Touch Me (film)|Touch Me]]''\n| 1997\n| Counselor\n|\n|\n|-\n|''[[What Planet Are You From?]]''\n| rowspan=4|2000\n| Doreen\n|\n|\n|-\n|''Red Lipstick''\n| Final TV Newscaster\n|\n|\n|-\n|''Color Me Gay''\n| Executive / Do-Rag Lesbian\n| Finalist at the 2nd PlanetOut.com Short Movie Awards\n|\n|-\n|''[[Best in Show (film)|Best in Show]]''\n| Christy Cummings\n|\n|\n|-\n|''Martini''\n| rowspan=2|2001\n| Dr. Jane\n|rowspan=3|Short film\n|\n|-\n|''Nice Guys Finish Last''\n| Mom\n|\n|-\n|''Hiding in Walls''\n| rowspan=2|2002\n| Diane Moffet\n|\n|-\n|''[[Collateral Damage (film)|Collateral Damage]]''\n| Agent Russo\n|\n|\n|-\n|''[[A Mighty Wind]]''\n| rowspan=2|2003\n| Laurie Bohner\n| [[Florida Film Critics Circle Award for Best Cast]]<br />Nominated\u2014Phoenix Film Critics Society Award for Best Cast\n|\n|-\n|''[[Exposed (2003 film)|Exposed]]''\n| Julie Gross\n|\n|\n|-\n|''Little Black Boot''\n| rowspan=6|2004