]]''\n| 2018\n| Sergeant Tamora Jean Calhoun\n| rowspan=2|Voice role\n|\n|-\n|''[[UglyDolls]]''\n| 2019\n| Scanner, Electronic Voice\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1992\n| ''[[In the Best Interest of the Children]]''\n| Gwen Hatcher\n| Television film; as Janey Lynch\n|-\n|rowspan=2|1993\n| ''[[Bakersfield P.D.]]''\n| Michelle Hathaway\n| \"Bakersfield Madam\"\n|-\n| ''[[Empty Nest]]''\n| Tammy\n| \"The Girl Who Cried Baby\"\n|-\n|rowspan=3|1994\n| ''[[Married... with Children]]''\n| Greta\n| \"Valentine's Day Massacre\"\n|-\n| ''[[Party of Five]]''\n| Dr. Pennant\n|  \"Much Ado\"\n|-\n| ''[[The John Larroquette Show]]''\n| Evaluator\n| \"The Tutor\"\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1995\n| ''[[In the House (TV series)|In The House]]''\n| Ruth\n| \"Female Trouble\"\n|-\n| ''[[NewsRadio]]''\n| Carol\n| \"The Cane\"\n|-\n| rowspan=3|1996\n| ''[[Cybill]]''\n| Mrs. Sweeney\n| \"Educating Zoey\"\n|-\n| ''[[3rd Rock from the Sun]]''\n| Mrs. Koppel\n| \"Dick, Smoker\"\n|-\n| ''[[Frasier]]''\n| Cynthia\n| \"A Lilith Thanksgiving\"\n|-\n| 1998\n| ''[[Caroline in the City]]''\n| Hostess\n| \"Caroline and the First Date\"  \n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[Dharma & Greg]]''\n| Sheryl\n|  \"Play Lady Play\"\n|-\n| 1999\u20132000\n| ''[[Judging Amy]]''\n| ASA Perkins\n| \"Pilot\", |Drawing the Line\" & \"Waterworld\"\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2000\n| ''[[JAG (TV series)|JAG]]''\n|Sandy's Friend\n| \"The Witches of Gulfport\"\n|-\n| ''[[Gilmore Girls]]''\n| Nurse\n|  \"Forgiveness and Stuff\"\n|-\n| 2000 & 2001\n| ''[[The West Wing]]''\n| Reporter\n| \"In the Shadow of Two Gunmen: Part I\" & \"Two Cathedrals\"\n|-\n| rowspan=9|2001\n| ''[[Dawson's Creek]]''\n| Mrs. Witter\n|  \"The Te of Pacey\"\n|-\n| ''[[Cursed (TV show)|Cursed]]''\n| Carla\n|  \"...And Then Jack Had Two Dates\"\n|-\n| ''[[Popular (TV series)|Popular]]''\n| Susie Klein\n|  \"I Know What You Did Last Spring Break\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Division]]''\n|\n| \